column5: I am always on the go as if driven by a motor.
column7: It's hard for me to stay in one place very long.
column8: It's hard for me to keep track of several things at once.
column10: I have a short fuse/hot temper.
column12: I avoid new challenges because I lack faith in my abilities.
column13: I seek out fast paced, exciting activities.
column14: I feel restless inside even if I am sitting still.
column15: Things I hear or see distract me from what I'm doing.
column16: Many things set me off easily.
column19: I act okay on the outside, but inside I'm unsure of myself.
column20: I can't get things done unless there's an absolute deadline.
column21: I have trouble getting started on a task.
column25: Sometimes my attention narrows so much that I'm oblivious to everything else; other times it's so broad that everything distracts me.
column26: I tend to squirm or fidget.
column27: I can't keep my mind on something unless it's really interesting.
column28: I wish I had greater confidence in my abilities.
column29: My past failures make it hard for me to believe in myself.
